{"tid":855952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"禁電子煙就係立23條嘅前奏","createTime":"2018-10-10T10:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T11:46:50.000Z","uid":104130,"like":11,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"21248fe594d8c344073abb4890a4ddc70135b769","tid":855952,"uid":104130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T10:36:51.000Z","msg":"項莊舞劍，志在沛公。梁振英見到隔離post咁多正評一定笑到瞓唔着覺<br />\n<br />\n好多連登仔要禁煙嘅邏輯，同啲廢佬反對港獨其實無分別。<br />\n<br />\n禁賣電子煙之後，他日你用咩理據反對23條？<br />\n<br />\n食唔食電子煙係每個人嘅選擇，賣唔賣電子煙都只係自由市場底下嘅正常商業活動，點解政府要管？<br />\n<br />\n政治立場係每個人嘅選擇，討論港獨亦都只係言論自由同學術自由嘅一部份，點解政府要管？<br />\n<br />\n大家繼續支持禁煙，反對港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：非煙民，學術討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59744c27525d0bac6e91261c18bad261118cd413","tid":855952,"uid":39064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T10:41:39.000Z","msg":"新加坡禁香口膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df65be92c53d6c915f89b8dbdb85cf03ba8c8755","tid":855952,"uid":167832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T10:45:17.000Z","msg":"依支嫣又算不算<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181010/58778827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58778827&d=mbpCeGZ7F5pg7ap3sWC%2FOjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=69a90d85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58778827&h=b64eb99f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181010/58778827</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廉署起訴李偲嫣舞弊 涉違法處置不明來歷選舉捐贈"},{"pid":"7c6c77c